<dl id="n12133b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12133b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12133b"> 133(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> the sweating stone</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Il naquit sur une pierre qui se couvre d&apos;eau si l&apos;on fait un parjure aupr&egrave;s d&apos;elle. <br><font color="green">[He was born upon a stone which became covered with water if one committed perjury near it.]</font> <small> Georges Dottin, <a name="GDSP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#GDSP"><cite title="source">Les livres de Saint Patrick, ap&ocirc;tre de l'Irlande</cite></a> (n.d) 12</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
